      "blocks": {
        "item_wxPJpr": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "2012",
            "text": "<p>Born from garage heatwaves, Della began with a simple idea: comfort should be easier to access and simpler to trust. That belief became a mission to bring reliable cooling to more homes.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_14453.png"
          }
        },
        "item_meDdTU": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "2015",
            "text": "<p>With a new Los Angeles warehouse, faster delivery and broader access brought reliable comfort closer to more homes.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sylro_Portable_AC_9_40c32386-f755-41d9-bddb-3415601884a3.jpg"
          }
        },
        "item_W4JyWb": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "2018-2020",
            "text": "<p>As homes evolved, Della introduced mini split systems and expanded distribution in South Carolina, helping more households enjoy room-by-room comfort built for modern living.</p>",
            "video": "shopify://files/videos/Creating the perfect reading sanctuary in my living room with the DELLA 42’’ Ultra Quiet Smart T.mp4"
          }
        },
        "item_3UdhGk": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "2022-2024",
            "text": "<p>With growing trust from homeowners nationwide, Della refreshed its brand, expanded in Texas, enhanced the Della+ app, and became a leading mini split choice on Amazon.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Sylro_Portable_AC_4.jpg"
          }
        },
        "item_TdwkA9": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "title": "2025 & beyond",
            "text": "<p>Della entered its next chapter with the launch of Central AC systems, Red Dot award-winning design, and a partnership with the LA Galaxy to bring smarter comfort to more local homes.</p>",
